Mbali chinyamkela hezakwingila umo bule, wala munhu yoyose yotenda mbuli za chinyala hebu uvwizi. Ila wawo muhala wokwingila waja mazina yawo yandikigwa muna ichitabu cha ugima cha Mwanang'hondolo.
